@DATABASE "Pacmania"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - P - Pacmania"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - P
                   ====================================

                                 Pacmania
                                 ========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34502,128)"}          34502,x (x= 1-128)
@{"Infinite Lives" rxs "address command zxampoke(35141,0)"}          35141,0
@{"Turbo Pacman  " rxs "address command zxampoke(34526,0)"}          34526,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
